{"tid":642514,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"顯耀邨男子上吊 送院不治","createTime":"2018-04-25T23:45:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-26T02:21:22.000Z","uid":41404,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e847e29cf7866b4e741eb3bcd4c669f16e17199d","tid":642514,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T23:45:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180426/large/1524699003_eebb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180426%2Flarge%2F1524699003_eebb.jpg&h=b09bc41a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n 上吊尼龍繩。<br />\n<br />\n早上近6時，沙田顯耀邨顯耀樓，保安員巡樓至36至37梯間，發現一名男子用木椅墊高及用尼龍繩上吊，立即報警。消防員到場將事主解下，送院搶救證實不治。<br />\n<br />\n死者60歲，據稱患有癌症，疑因病輕生。警方調查事件無可疑。<br />\n<br />\n24小時求助熱線︰<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會熱線︰23892222<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)︰28960000<br />\n生命熱線︰23820000<br />\n東華三院芷若園熱線︰18281<br />\n社會福利署熱線︰23432255<br />\n醫院管理局精神健康專線(24小時精神健康熱線諮詢服務)：24667350<br />\n明愛向晴熱線：18288"},{"pid":"819dbd6a1b97e179a0a275060d14c44124b4f3ed","tid":642514,"uid":69886,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T23:45:30.000Z","msg":"抵撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12212a546ab2766a4d4bc0de92b64559dd893daf","tid":642514,"uid":6845,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T23:45:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ab77690ab79c38837339951b3420a5e8e404809","tid":642514,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T23:47:02.000Z","msg":"60歲關我撚事咩"},{"pid":"0c5d2529f78e242842e4998e765e28e8680bc51f","tid":642514,"uid":40470,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"819dbd6a1b97e179a0a275060d14c44124b4f3ed","tid":642514,"uid":69886,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T23:45:30.000Z","msg":"抵撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"